UMA ungenaso isitifikethi somsebenzi wokuqapha izikhulu emikhakheni ehlukene, phecelezi ibodyguard, cabanga ngenye indlela. Lesi sitifikethi uma wenza umsebenzi wokuba ngunogada sikuvulela amadlalelo aluhlaza kangangokuthi kwesinye isikhathi ugcina usuthole umsebenzi kweminye iminyango kahulumeni. Ngaphandle kwalokho ngeke uyikhalele imali yakho oyisebenzise ufunda, ngoba ibuya isiphindwe kaningi, futhi lomsebenzi ubukeka uhamba phambili kulesi sikhathi. Woza eKhanyisani Training Academy, ePinetown entshonalanga yeTheku. Lesi sikhungo singesinye sezikhungo ezichonywa uphaphe legwalagwala uma kukhulunywa ngezikhungo eziqeqesha ama-Bodyguard aqashekayo futhi awenza ngokukhulu ukuzimisela nokuwuhlonipha umsebenzi wawo. Abasebenzi balesi sikhungo bayazimisela emsebenzini wabo futhi bayaqikelela ukuthi konke abakwenzayo bafuna ugculiseke. Bayaqinisekisa ukuthi bakhuluma ulimi ozwana nalo. Ikilasi elilandelayo kulindeleke ukuthi libe ngoMsombuluko, kaJuni 21, emahhovisi alesi sikhungo eMdoni Centre, emgwaqweni uCrompton, ngenhla kwaseposini ePinetown noma ushayele ku-031 7019284 ukuthola kabanzi. Uma ufuna ukuba yingxenye yaleli kilasi kubalulekile ukuthi ubhalise kuseyimanje ngoba izikhala ezikhona zanele abantu abalishumi kuphela. Kuningi nokunye okuwusizo ongakuthola uma usufikile kungenjalo vakashela ikhasi lika-facebook elithi: khanyisanitrainingacademy.